			<p>I was deeply moved by Heather Sellers&rsquo;s essay &ldquo;<a href="/article/4114">The Wizard in the Closet</a>&rdquo; [December 2007], about her mentor. I, too, teach college-level writing, and I feel that I carry several of my former teachers with me into the classroom each day.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Kristin Van Tassel<br>Lindsborg, Kansas</p>
					</blockquote>
